{"tid":2429563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細態度突然改變係咩先兆","createTime":"2021-03-02T11:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T12:25:20.000Z","uid":138834,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8643d336c130562f124c3031f72cd79fc7b1f231","tid":2429563,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"以前同老細啲關係一路都係淡如水<br />\n佢一句指示，我一句收到/ok就完<br />\n大家語氣都好似機械咁<br />\n<br />\n近排佢語氣變到好撚親切<br />\n好似我先係老細咁<br />\n仲成日講啲唔好笑嘅笑話（平時極少）<br />\n開工利是又大封左，往年50，今年500<br />\n<br />\n但近排我明明冇為公司作出過咩巨大貢獻<br />\n反而前排開口叫佢加人工（加左）<br />\n<br />\n重點係，我同啲同事八完，發現佢對其他同事個態度冇變<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以解釋下<br />\n<br />\n依家同佢講電話時有種好噁心嘅感覺，會打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec48ab76177b83abf27cecda6e04b2a2e81bd81","tid":2429563,"uid":158145,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:44:03.000Z","msg":"公司炒人有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6df69980cdee408c8a75d4619b7e635ff3fa65","tid":2429563,"uid":102716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2367a21a62dab4d0e10a4342438dca49ec1fb2","tid":2429563,"uid":138834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6ec48ab76177b83abf27cecda6e04b2a2e81bd81","tid":2429563,